  "comment": "LUMI4COMPAQ is a plug & play portable LED wash light set for lighting mobile stages and clubs. LUMI4COMPAQ is made up of a lighting bar with 4 LEDs projectors, each one equipped with 3x9 W high-power RGB / FC LEDs. LED technology allows these luminaires to create striking effects with dynamic colour changes, powerful and synchronised operations. The power and the control unit is contained inside the light-bar, the system also includes a footswitch, a tripod stand and a comfortable travel bag.",
